## Monorepo Architecture

### Workspace Structure

```
scani/
├── apps/
│   ├── backend/              # Node/Bun backend application
│   ├── frontendV2/           # React web frontend (Vite)
│   ├── mobile/               # React Native mobile app (Expo)
│   └── landing/              # Marketing landing page
├── packages/
│   └── (future shared packages)
├── .specify/                 # Project specifications and memory
│   └── memory/
│       └── constitution.md   # Non-negotiable principles
└── package.json              # Root workspace configuration
```

### Backend Architecture (Clean Architecture)

```
apps/backend/src/
├── domain/
│   └── entities/             # Core business entities (User, Account, Holding, etc.)
├── application/
│   ├── services/             # Business logic services (AccountService, PricingService)
│   └── use-cases/            # Complex operations (CreateHoldingsWithDependenciesUseCase)
├── infrastructure/
│   ├── database/             # Drizzle schema, migrations, connection
│   ├── repositories/         # Data access layer (extends BaseRepository)
│   └── external-services/    # Third-party integrations (AI, blockchain, pricing)
└── presentation/
    ├── routers/              # tRPC router definitions
    ├── middleware/           # Auth, rate limiting, CORS
    └── trpc.ts               # tRPC initialization
```

**Dependency Flow**: Domain ← Application ← Infrastructure ← Presentation

### Web Frontend Structure

```
apps/frontendV2/src/
├── components/
│   ├── features/             # Feature-specific components
│   ├── layout/               # Layout components
│   ├── selectors/            # Data selector components
│   └── ui/                   # Reusable UI components (Shadcn)
├── contexts/                 # React Context providers
├── hooks/                    # Custom React hooks
├── lib/                      # Utilities and helpers
├── pages/                    # Route-level components
└── trpc.ts                   # tRPC client setup
```

### Mobile App Structure (Ignite Pattern)

```
apps/mobile/src/
├── app/                      # Expo Router file-based routes
│   ├── _layout.tsx           # Root layout with providers
│   └── (tabs)/               # Tab navigation group
├── components/               # Reusable components
├── screens/                  # Screen components
├── theme/                    # Ignite theme system
│   ├── colors.ts             # Color palette (light)
│   ├── colorsDark.ts         # Color palette (dark)
│   ├── spacing.ts            # Spacing scale
│   ├── typography.ts         # Font definitions
│   └── context.tsx           # Theme provider
├── i18n/                     # Internationalization
│   ├── en.ts                 # English translations
│   └── ru.ts                 # Russian translations
├── services/
│   ├── trpc/                 # tRPC client setup
│   └── supabase/             # Supabase auth client
└── utils/                    # Utilities and helpers
```

### Shared Packages

Currently types are imported directly from backend workspace via `@scani/backend`. Future shared packages will be created in `packages/` directory.

