## Key Principles Summary

1. **End-to-End Type Safety**: TypeScript strict mode, tRPC, Drizzle ORM, Zod validation - no runtime surprises
2. **Clean Architecture**: Dependency injection, repository pattern, use cases - maintainable and testable
3. **Mobile-First Quality**: Ignite theming, i18n, offline-first - production-grade mobile experience
4. **Testing Excellence**: 93%+ coverage, TDD, real database testing - confidence in every change
5. **Security by Design**: JWT auth, data isolation, secure storage - privacy-focused and compliant
6. **Observability**: Structured logging, Sentry tracking, performance monitoring - production-ready from day one

